What you need to know:

Kamworor who the RAK Half Marathon title in 2013 was unable to defend his World Half Marathon title in Poland on October 17 last year due to the accident. Kamworor has  won the world half marathon title thrice in 2014, 2016 and 2018.Uganda’s Jacob Kiplimo cashed in on Kamworor’s absence to win the Poland race in a Championship Record (CR) time of 58:49 as Kandie settled for silver also inside the CR time in 58:54.